A list of the greatest works of literature on this planet.

============================================================

The Foundation Trilogy                 --  Isaac Asimov
The Gods Themselves                    --  Isaac Asimov
Dune Series                            --  Frank Herbert
The Neverending Story                  --  Michael Ende
The Passage Trilogy                    --  Justin Cronin
The Hitchiker's Guide to the Galaxy    --  Douglas Adams
Childhood's End                        --  Arthur C. Clarke
2001: A Space Odyssey Series           --  Arthur C. Clarke
Rendezvous With Rama                   --  Arthur C. Clarke
Seveneves                              --  Neal Stephenson
Snow Crash                             --  Neal Stephenson
Diamond Age                            --  Neal Stephenson
Neuromancer                            --  William Gibson
Fight Club                             --  Chuck Palahniuk
Damned                                 --  Chuck Palahniuk
Doomed                                 --  Chuck Palahniuk
Invisible Monsters                     --  Chuck Palahniuk
A Canticle For Leibowitz               --  Walter M. Miller
1984                                   --  George Orwell
Brave New World                        --  Aldous Huxley
Ender's Game                           --  Orson Scott Card
Interstellar                           --  Greg Keyes
Do Androids Dream of Electric Sheep    --  Philip K. Dick
Otherland Trilogy                      --  Tad Williams
Ready Player One                       --  Ernest Cline
Leviathan Wakes (Expanse Series)       --  James S. A. Corey
Moonwalking With Einstein              --  Joshua Foer
The Martian                            --  Andy Weir
Sapiens: A Brief History of Humankind  --  Yuval Noah Harari
